    "body": "https://github.com/starship/starship/blob/f7d583821a01d2429cef1f243228aa04055f4760/src/main.rs#L35\n\nRename this to `Powershell` may solve the problem. Or you can use a `#[value(alias(\"powershell\"))]` on this variant.\n\nIf a suggestion is needed, you can add a separate `Powershell` variant and replace:\n\nhttps://github.com/starship/starship/blob/f7d583821a01d2429cef1f243228aa04055f4760/src/main.rs#L53\n\ninto:\n\n```rust\nCompletionShell::PowerShell => { generate_shell(clap_complete::Shell::PowerShell); eprintln!(\"...\"); }\nCompletionShell::Powershell => generate_shell(clap_complete::Shell::PowerShell),\n```",
